title: Tip #1
body: Leave your coat and boots at the airport before heading for warmer climates. Coat check and storage services are available at the information desk.

title: Tip #2
body: Reserve and pay for parking at YQB up to 24 hours before you plan on arriving at the airport.

title: Tip #4
body: Stay connected with free Wi-Fi throughout the terminal any time you are at the airport.

title: Tip #3
body: Check in and print your boarding pass up to 24 hours before your departure using the self-serve check-in kiosks in the terminal.
